{"type":"answer","id":104648,"parentType":"question","parentId":13261,"uid":15246,"contents":"觀察上海某郊區的農民，以村為單位有不少是同一個姓氏，村委會也是本地村民選出；<br>\n“民主？”<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CvCT6Hj.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CvCT6Hj.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/CvCT6Hj.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n由於徵地的緣故，普遍比較富裕，基本的公共開支例如倒垃圾、清理街道等項目，有充足的資金；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kxilGE6.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kxilGE6.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kxilGE6.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n村委會同時也有資金進行投資，村民每年都有分紅，村民多數在市區都有房；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n大陸其他地方的農村估計很少達到這樣的程度。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/vCdIOqO.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vCdIOqO.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/vCdIOqO.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-14","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}